Jose LATA, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Daniel LOUGHLIN and/or Kelly Loughlin, and Millstone Valley General Construction, Defendants,
and
Waitikowich Construction Inc., Defendant-Respondent. C-764 September Term 2018
082257 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 4, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001129-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
